text: Fabienne Pascaud (born July 1, 1955) is a journalist, critic, and editor in chief for French publication Télérama. She is best known for her theater criticism. ==References== Category:1955 births Category:Living people Category:20th-century French writers Category:21st-century French writers Category:French critics Category:French women writers Category:French journalists Category:Chevaliers of the Légion d'honneur Category:People from Paris
